{"data":{"wpPage":{"title":"Careers","content":"\n<p>For more than three decades, FLS has grown from a niche projects company to a versatile, global organization involved in logistics, warehousing, and trading with more than 300 employees across eleven countries. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our passion for supply chain solutions, a dynamic team attitude and individual growth set us apart from others. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>We aim to build on this successful history and are always looking for highly motivated and talented people to join us on our journey of success. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"workplace-culture\"><strong>WORKPLACE &amp; CULTURE</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"diversity-and-inclusion\"><strong>Diversity and Inclusion</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>At FLS, we want to build a second home where everyone has an equal opportunity to excel and contribute to the success of the company &#8211; regardless of disability, race, religious beliefs, cultures, gender, sexual orientations, and perspectives.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As a growing company, we recognise that the diversity of our workforce is an important aspect as we bring talents together; each with their unique background, ability and character. As a team working together and collaborating with internal stakeholders and the external community, we ensure that working environments and conditions in all offices are conducive for every employee to be part of the FLS family.</p>\n","careerSpotlight":{"spotlightContent":"<p>We put a spotlight on our greatest assets: our people.</p>\n","spotlight":[{"spotlightName":"Thip","spotlightRole":"Logistics Manager at FLS Solutions Thailand","quote":"“Thip is an absolute pillar of our organisation. Her calm and methodical approach to any task at hand keeps our backs free, because we know she is taking care of things and we can always rely on her support. She is just great to work with and is well liked by everyone in the team.” ","fromName":"Christoph Campbell","fromRole":"Managing Director, FLS Trading","spotlightThumbnail":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"backgroundColor":"transparent","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/a6955d44d4875badf78714aeefbde78b/4164c/Thip.jpg","srcSet":"/static/a6955d44d4875badf78714aeefbde78b/4164c/Thip.jpg 425w,\n/static/a6955d44d4875badf78714aeefbde78b/cc812/Thip.jpg 729w","sizes":"(min-width: 425px) 425px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/a6955d44d4875badf78714aeefbde78b/e1e78/Thip.webp 425w,\n/static/a6955d44d4875badf78714aeefbde78b/efe9a/Thip.webp 729w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 425px) 425px, 100vw"}]},"width":425,"height":425}}}}},{"spotlightName":"Khun Som-O Sudalak Sattayabundit","spotlightRole":"FLS Warehousing","quote":"\"Khun Som-O is a key player in the founding team of FLS Warehousing. She brings a smile to everyone’s face. A bit 'tingtong' (crazy, in Thai) but also a professional lady who goes the extra mile for our customers.\"","fromName":"Marcel Kirschnick","fromRole":"Global Director Logistics","spotlightThumbnail":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"backgroundColor":"transparent","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/70ec42174a702081ec1aab6cc9706511/4164c/Khun-Som-O-Sudalak-Sattayabundit.jpg","srcSet":"/static/70ec42174a702081ec1aab6cc9706511/4164c/Khun-Som-O-Sudalak-Sattayabundit.jpg 425w,\n/static/70ec42174a702081ec1aab6cc9706511/c3b72/Khun-Som-O-Sudalak-Sattayabundit.jpg 720w","sizes":"(min-width: 425px) 425px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/70ec42174a702081ec1aab6cc9706511/e1e78/Khun-Som-O-Sudalak-Sattayabundit.webp 425w,\n/static/70ec42174a702081ec1aab6cc9706511/6743d/Khun-Som-O-Sudalak-Sattayabundit.webp 720w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 425px) 425px, 100vw"}]},"width":425,"height":425}}}}},{"spotlightName":"Nataraj Ganapathy","spotlightRole":"Overseas Delegate for FLS in India","quote":"\"Nataraj’s bravery truly impresses me. He joined FLS during the worst period of the Covid-19 pandemic as our Overseas Delegate in India - basically, as a “one-man-show”. Despite the unpredictable economy, he embraced the challenge from day one and his pro-activeness and persistence quickly brought us some excellent business results. I am proud of what he has achieved and very happy to have him on our team.\"","fromName":"Marcel Kirschnick","fromRole":"Global Director Logistics","spotlightThumbnail":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"backgroundColor":"transparent","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/4164c/Nataraj-post.jpg","srcSet":"/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/4164c/Nataraj-post.jpg 425w,\n/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/e4d02/Nataraj-post.jpg 750w,\n/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/4d335/Nataraj-post.jpg 1080w,\n/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/43755/Nataraj-post.jpg 1366w,\n/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/583c4/Nataraj-post.jpg 1500w","sizes":"(min-width: 425px) 425px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/e1e78/Nataraj-post.webp 425w,\n/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/cd166/Nataraj-post.webp 750w,\n/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/4dfd9/Nataraj-post.webp 1080w,\n/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/aaaac/Nataraj-post.webp 1366w,\n/static/ac1da2e0ea18dfaad4ad951c4eef727c/fa658/Nataraj-post.webp 1500w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 425px) 425px, 100vw"}]},"width":425,"height":425}}}}},{"spotlightName":"Quoc Trung","spotlightRole":"Port Captain, FLS Vietnam","quote":"\"Trung's close relationships with local vendors, authorities and fabricators along with his technical and nautical background makes him invaluable. Thanks to him we minimize the risk of cargo mishandling and damages and control the daily operational costs on the ground. On top of that, he's a really great guy.\"\r\n","fromName":"Christopher Schnieders","fromRole":"Global Director Projects & CMO","spotlightThumbnail":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"backgroundColor":"transparent","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/25f9dc6d5ea549ab2bd55c9afe4dceb3/4164c/trung1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/25f9dc6d5ea549ab2bd55c9afe4dceb3/4164c/trung1.jpg 425w,\n/static/25f9dc6d5ea549ab2bd55c9afe4dceb3/e4d02/trung1.jpg 750w,\n/static/25f9dc6d5ea549ab2bd55c9afe4dceb3/d9377/trung1.jpg 853w","sizes":"(min-width: 425px) 425px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/25f9dc6d5ea549ab2bd55c9afe4dceb3/e1e78/trung1.webp 425w,\n/static/25f9dc6d5ea549ab2bd55c9afe4dceb3/cd166/trung1.webp 750w,\n/static/25f9dc6d5ea549ab2bd55c9afe4dceb3/92484/trung1.webp 853w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 425px) 425px, 100vw"}]},"width":425,"height":425}}}}}]}}}}